To further confirm the difference in Dit between the emitter SiN layer and p-Si substrate after HDH treatment in Fig. 5, the Al/SiN/p-Si/Al metal-insulator-semiconductor (MIS) structure is fabricated. Since the SiN and p-Si interface has a large amount of defects, the G-V result can be applied to extract the interface trap density (Dit) [24]. The conductance equation is given as:
